Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready for your repentance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,542)}Photon Stream of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faker...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks won't make it past a genius mind like mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! This is Heart eartH's true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 92! Heart eartH Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why on earth is there a new Number on his field!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain it to you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:01:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Heart-eartH has no Overlay Units while being attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by using Heart-eartH as an Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon Heart-eartH Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when this Monster has been Special Summoned successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all opposing Attack Position Monsters\Nare changed into Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you were fools to try to fight back against a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow down before Heart-eartH Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So our Monsters were changed to Defense Mode before the damage could reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why the attack stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It still had an effect like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go. Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake Form!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your Monsters have been changed into Defense Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this card deals you 400 damage for each Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take 1200 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Kuriphoton's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sending this card from my hand to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and paying half of my Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Effect Damage is negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is your body...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to break down yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until I have defeated you, Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had you been defeated, you would not have had to suffer on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will defeat you?" Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your defeat is coming closer step by step,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,heralding the extinction of the Astral World!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart-eartH Dragon, attack Shark Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's attacking with Zero Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is Heart-eartH Dragon not destroyed in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I Battle Damage against me is negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you guys receive the original damage in my stead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using a Zero Attack Power Monster to attack the 2100 Defense Power Shark Drake,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the result is 2100 from the original damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all negated on his end and bounced back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Life is a mere 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get hit by 2100 damage...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Heart Break Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too soon for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you! Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape Lure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,423)}"Numbers 70: The Terrifying, Most Sinister Dragon Appears!\N The False Skeletal God Dragon, Heart-eartH Dragon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card changes the attack target to a different Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and halves the resulting Battle Damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I change the attack target to Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! There's no sense in doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he choosing Hope as the attack target?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we reduce that guy's damage, our damage will be reduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Half Unbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card halves the Battle Damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(613,526)}I will use this effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,530)}on Heart-eartH Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,530)}You used the Trap to protect my Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! By reducing the damage you would receive,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the damage sent back to us is reduced as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way the damage for Heart-eartH Dragon is 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we only take 500 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch... Useless struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I will activate another effect of Heart-eartH Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is the Battle Damage inflicted on me negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I gain that amount of Life instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys... Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hope is.... resting on you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Ryouga. You braved this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still patronizing even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... Our Life is down to 100 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to whine, lie down there and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... I-I'm not whining at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like heck will I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral is waiting for me to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely... rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope will be the Xyz Material!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Xyz Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The messenger who changes chaos into light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Chaos Number 39!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Numbers. The new power of the Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something like that won't beat my Heart-eartH Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure, Heart-eartH Dragon can negate attacks,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and bounce back the damage to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... I'm sure there's something in my hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think... think hard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword Chaos Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finally make up your mind\Nto throw your life down the drain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given up at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand, I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Gamusharush!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Gamusharush, I can set the Attack Power of my battling Monster to zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the opposing player will receive 600 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You actually put a bit of thought into that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If attacks won't work, you just reduce his Life with effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being way too reckless for a mere 600 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of our bonds, we {\i1}will{\i0} beat this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a bit longer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, the effect of Heart-eartH Dragon activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this monster was special summoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all cards then Summoned or set on the opponent's field...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be Banished on the next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Hope Ray is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonds, you say? Such stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like that are merely an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it really exists, show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you call the "power of your bonds".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that you can't actually {\i1}see{\i0} the bonds you share with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're something deep down within your heart that connects with another's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they exist, our feelings always will reach one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Marine Biting Shark Drake, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Chaos Xyz Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Shark Drake as Xyz Material, I Special Summon a Chaos Number!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Chaos Number 32!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Biting Marine Serpent Shark Drake Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't give up either. I'll it to show him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My own way to 'Bring it to 'em!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Deep Sea Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, I send a Water-Attribute Monster with 2000 or more Attack Points from my hand to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and on this turn, one Monster on my field can attack the opponent directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I send Jawsman to the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, Shark Drake Weiss can attack directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Drake Weiss, direct attack on Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depth Chaos Bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He avoided Heart-eartH Dragon by attacking Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can negate the damage from a direct attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then let me recover that amount of Life Points instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn Faker increased his Life Points again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and my tu-...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryouga,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Byron's scheme, you lost your pride and your younger sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and now you're going to lose {\i1}yourself{\i0} in the most pathetic way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark! Hey, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're injured?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryouga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings... I've received all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't seem to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart-eartH Dragon's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cards will be Banished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear, Shark Drake Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now try to prove it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What those bonds of yours are all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this moment, Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Xyz-Dimension Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card gets Banished by my opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon two Level Eight Water-Attribute Monsters from my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trap that activates when it's Banished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon two Ancient Shark Hyper Megalodons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effects of the Monsters Summoned by this effect are negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they can neither attack nor be released!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you took advantage of Heart-eartH Dragon's effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}did{\i0} say our feelings would definitely reach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm entrusting you... with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryouga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Eight Galaxy-Eyes and the two Hyper Megalodons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network with these three Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Galaxy of Reversal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become the rolling waves of light and show your mighty form!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Descend, my very soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't break down yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Ryouga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo Galaxy-Eyes' effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this Monster has been Summoned successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the effects of all other Monsters on the field are negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Howling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the effects of Heart-eartH Dragon are negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, by detaching one Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all Overlay Units from all other Monsters on the field will be absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for this turn, its Attack Power will
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,increase by 500 points for each Overlay Unit absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5000 Attack Points?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker, I will redeem you with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready for your repentance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You're just a clueless brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Photon Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! Faker just got some big damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, Dr. Faker. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release Haruto {\i1}now{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you... have any idea what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way for Haruto to survive is to destroy the Astral World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the power of Barian, there is no way now Haruto can survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto was a frail child ever since he was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, his flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is so small, it might vanish in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, in order to save his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I just had to visit the Parallel Worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, Dad and Tron were...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I decided to save Haruto, I gave up everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends and partners...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byron and Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to sacrifice them to be able to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting on the other side of the door was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Substance does not exist within their world.\N It is a world made up of some kind of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They show no ability of metaphysics in their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To give Haruto the power he needs to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to destroy the Astral World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I started collecting the Numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to use their power in the Sphere Field Cannon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I had planned to destroy the Astral World with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't keep my promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sooner or later these guys will come to take Haruto away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's really the truth, then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I would have told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would have tried to burden the bitter fate all on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was grateful, Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without complaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you fought for Haruto as Number Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want to make you suffer any more than you already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you believe in your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you believe in them and not trust in me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they come to take away Haruto's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Haruto!\NI will protect him to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it costs my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, I will lend you my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about these Barian guys, but I will beat them to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to settle with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush them for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the three of us joining forces, Barian won't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:20:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to give up anything anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just believe in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll settle this with them once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker... how regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Dad!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you could do better than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Number is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo. Kaito Tenjo. Ryouga Kamishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel hasn't been settled yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0}... Barian.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Barian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.68,0:23:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barian has finally appeared in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ran out of answers, being cornered by his overwhelming power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:23:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hope and our future...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we give them up like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, I'll come to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our power, we will raise it to the ultimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me power, ZEXAL Weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Miraculous 'Bring it to 'Em'!\NOpen a Path to the Future, ZEXAL!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.87,0:24:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the feelings everyone has entrusted to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Ray, Shark Drake Weiss, and Neo Galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.73,0:24:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the sum of their Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Ray's is 39, Shark Drake's is 32 and Neo Galaxy-Eyes is... umm....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is 71, because Neo Galaxy isn't a Number.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.40,0:24:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me...!
